  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n63\nNeeds Review\n63\n68 music is composed of -is - numbers Rightly, I seek beauty like Parsival sought the Grail - but what a price I pay. I don't write beautifulity - I just write reports about our conditing to go to those outside of (I'd pak. I am an anytyzer when I am attracted to marie laure (etc) I am attracted by God He takes this image to draw me along to my fulfillment, she is a way by which he appoachies me my wife. He wants me to go to france;",
      "matched_alias": "Grail",
      "term_id": "TERM_grail",
      "term_name": "Grail",
      "term_slug": "grail"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n65\nNeeds Review\n65\nt I'm a Soviet agent. Kathy she knew just as she knows about Bob/fred/bruce This is shes us but loved me why my house was hit. She led them around. No - the taco stand was us reprogramming involving Kathy had the info when I wrote huge pages I saw. \"Tears\" the all the philosophy + theology is due to Thomas' classical education a true Hegelian intellectual (+ Engels). The OCCP still wants the info from me - hence Joan + marie Laure. ",
      "matched_alias": "Hegelian",
      "term_id": "TERM_hegelian",
      "term_name": "Hegelian",
      "term_slug": "hegelian"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n\n61\nt 63 the freighted plasmate messages are from us half-lifers to those outside still alive King Felix: the rescuer is here t A sort of repair construct tih! To maintain our illusory world. It's a cube of water-like parts + fires form axes into the field + dialectic to create world, for us in cold pac. on a space ship the cube is basically projecting beauty then love. So: lave of the beautiful. It's just a light show of beauty to the dead, structere",
      "matched_alias": "Pyth",
      "term_id": "TERM_pyth",
      "term_name": "Pyth",
      "term_slug": "pyth"
    }
  ],
